Regular_polygon&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D1" title=3D"Edit section: G=
eneral properties"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-brack=
et">]</span></span></div>
<figure class=3D"skin-invert-image" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"htt=
