<p>For a regular <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=
n</span>-gon, the sum of the perpendicular distances from any interior poin=
t to the <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>=
