<p><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coxeter" class=3D"mw-redirect" =
title=3D"Coxeter">Coxeter</a> states that every <a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Zonogon" title=3D"Zonogon">zonogon</a> (a 2<i>m</i>-gon whose=
 opposite sides are parallel and of equal length) can be dissected into <sp=
an class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-ma=
th-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=
=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle {\tbinom =
{m}{2}}}">
