box-text-span">This section <b>needs expansion</b>. You can help by <a clas=
s=3D"external text" href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DRe=
gular_polygon&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D">adding to it</a>.  <span cl=
